elderly /ˈɛldəlɪ/

1. ADJ You use elderly as a polite way of saying that someone is old. 上年纪的 [礼貌] 

例： There was an elderly couple on the terrace. 露台上有一对上年纪的老人。 

2. N-PLURAL The elderly are people who are old. 老年人 

